    "created_at": "2014-10-07T12:15:41Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-10-07T12:15:41Z",
    "body": "Unless we implement the XDG Trash Specification in atom-shell, we have to rely on external tools to implement `shell.MoveItemToTrash`, and `gvfs-trash` is already the safest guess. I think we should add `gvfs-bin` as dependency of the deb package instead of writing a lot of code to make `shell.MoveItemToTrash` work on all Linux distributions, so I'm closing this.\n"
